translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,107,"Agar Allah tujhey kisi museebat mein daley to khud uske siwa koi nahin jo is museebat ko taal de, aur agar woh tere haqq mein kisi bhalayi ka irada karey to uske fazal ko pherne wala bhi koi nahin hai. Woh apne bandon mein se jisko chahta hai apne fazal se nawazta hai aur woh darguzar karne wala aur reham farmane wala hai"
  10,108,"(Aey Muhammad), kehdo ke “logon , tumhare paas tumhare Rubb ki taraf se haqq aa chuka hai, ab jo seedhi raah ikhtiyar karey uski raast-rawi usi ke liye mufeed hai, aur jo gumraah rahey uski gumraahi usi ke liye tabah-kun hai. Aur main tumhare upar koi hawaladaar nahin hoon”"
  10,109,"Aur (aey Nabi), tum is hidayat ki pairwi kiye jao jo tumhari taraf bazariye wahee (revelation) bheji jaa rahi hai, aur sabr karo yahan tak ke Allah faisla karde, aur wahi behtareen faisla karne wala hai"
  11,1,"Alif Laam Raa. Farmaan hai , jiski aayatin pukhta aur mufassal irshad hui hain, ek dana(wise) aur bakhabar hasti ki taraf se"
  11,2,Ke tum na bandagi karo magar sirf Allah ki. Main uski taraf se tumko khabardaar karne wala bhi hoon aur basharat dene wala bhi
  11,3,Aur yeh ke tum apne Rubb se maafi chaho aur uski taraf palat aao to woh ek khaas muddat tak tumko accha samaan e zindagi dega aur har sahib-e-fazl ko uska fazal ata karega. Lekin agar tum mooh pherte ho to main tumhare haqq mein ek baday haulnaak din ke azaab se darta hoon
  11,4,Tum sabko Allah ki taraf palatna hai aur woh sab kuch kar sakta hai
  11,5,Dekho! Yeh log apne seeno ko moadte hain taa-ke ussey chup jayein. Khabardaar! Jab yeh kapdon se apne aap ko dhampte hain Allah unke chupe ko bhi jaanta hai aur khule ko bhi.Woh to un bhedon se bhi waqif hai jo seeno mein hain